          <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">ã‚‚ã†ã¡ã‚‡ã£ã¨é ­ä½¿ã£ãŸæ–¹ãŒã„ã„ã‚“ã˜ã‚ƒãªã„ã§ã™ã‹ï¼Ÿ</p>
          <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AIã®æ–¹ãŒåœ§å€’çš„ã«è³¢ã‹ã£ãŸã‚ˆã†ã§ã™ã­ã€œğŸ˜</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <p>ã‚ãªãŸã®æ•°å­—: <span style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb;">${playerTarget}</span></p>
            <p>AIã®æ•°å­—: <span style="font-family: monospace; font-weight: bold; color: #9333ea;">${aiTarget}</span></p>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #dc2626; margin-top: 1rem;">ğŸ¤¡ GAME OVER ğŸ¤¡</p>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 0.5rem;">æ¬¡ã¯é ‘å¼µã£ã¦ãã ã•ã„ã­ã€œï¼ˆç¬‘ï¼‰</p>
